            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯邦檢察官據悉對First Brands破產事件展開調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士透露，聯邦檢察官正在調查汽車零組件供應商First Brands Group驚人破產事件的相關情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該人士稱，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:司法部;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/司法部\">司法部</a>的調查仍處於初步階段。《金融時報》早些時候報導稱，此次司法部調查由曼哈頓聯邦檢察官辦公室負責。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">司法部與<span>First Brands</span>的發言人未立即回應置評請求。代表First Brands部分董事和公司所有者的律師未立即回覆尋求評論的信息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在放貸方對該公司用於管理日常現金流的賬外融資日益擔憂之後，First Brands於9月底陷入破產，並已經牽連多家大型金融機構。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bf2d5882-8c37-3a3e-ba75-8c83314218e0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Federal Prosecutors Are Looking Into First Brands Collapse</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Jonathan Randles.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E9%82%A6%E6%AA%A2%E5%AF%9F%E5%AE%98%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%B0%8Dfirst-brands%E7%A0%B4%E7%94%A2%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%B1%95%E9%96%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-204202525.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-10 05:15:51",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
